---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Boat & Rv Guardian | Premium Smart Monitoring">
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="hero-bg-glow"></div>
		<div class="container hero-container">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<h1 class="hero-title">An <span class="text-gradient">open-source platform</span> to monitor and control your vessel or rig's critical systems, whether you're onboard or miles away.</h1>
				<p class="hero-subtitle">
					Dead batteries mean failed bilge pumps. Burst pipes hooked to city water sink boats. Protect your vessel and RV with low-cost, off-the-shelf sensors and automatic shutoff valves.
				</p>
				<div class="hero-actions">
					<a href="#downloads" class="btn btn-primary">Download App</a>
					<a href="https://github.com/jgearinger/Boat-RV-Guardian" class="btn btn-outline">View on GitHub</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="hero-image-wrapper">
				<img src="/hero-dashboard.png" alt="Boat & Rv Guardian Dashboard Interface" class="hero-image" />
				<div class="glass-float float-1">
					<div class="float-icon">🔋</div>
					<div>
						<strong>House Battery</strong>
						<span class="status-ok">13.2V - Charging</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="glass-float float-2">
					<div class="float-icon">🚨</div>
					<div>
						<strong>High Water Sensor</strong>
						<span class="status-ok">Dry</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Downloads Section -->
	<section id="downloads" class="downloads-section container">
		<div class="section-header">
			<h2>Download the App</h2>
			<p>Boat & Rv Guardian is available on all major platforms. Download the latest release directly from our secure Cloudflare edge network.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="downloads-grid">
			<a href="https://downloads.boatrvguardian.com/boat-rv-guardian_latest.apk" class="glass-card download-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">📱</div>
				<h3>Android APK</h3>
				<p>Sideload the mobile app for on-the-go monitoring and instant push notifications.</p>
			</a>
			<a href="https://downloads.boatrvguardian.com/boat-rv-guardian_latest.dmg" class="glass-card download-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">🍎</div>
				<h3>macOS App</h3>
				<p>Native Apple Silicon and Intel desktop app for your navigation station.</p>
			</a>
			<a href="https://downloads.boatrvguardian.com/boat-rv-guardian_latest.exe" class="glass-card download-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">🪟</div>
				<h3>Windows App</h3>
				<p>Native Windows desktop app optimized for low-power onboard PCs.</p>
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Key Solutions Grid -->
	<section class="features-section container">
		<div class="section-header">
			<h2>The Value of Monitoring</h2>
			<p>Stop worrying about dead starter batteries or returning to a flooded cabin. Our Flow Tool (LinkTap) and low-cost Shelly sensors give you peace of mind whether you're off-grid or connected to endless city water.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="features-grid">
			<div class="glass-card feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">🔋</div>
				<h3>12V Power Monitoring</h3>
				<p>Keep a constant eye on your house batteries and shore power status using custom hardware integrations like the Shelly Uni.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">🌊</div>
				<h3>Smart Water Shutoff</h3>
				<p>Integration with LinkTap smart valves provides real-time flow metering and instant emergency shutoffs to prevent catastrophic floods.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">📡</div>
				<h3>Instant Cloud Alerts</h3>
				<p>Using Shelly sensors and Cloudflare Workers, our webhook receiver guarantees you get a push notification the second water is detected.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass-card feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">💻</div>
				<h3>Local API Mode</h3>
				<p>When you're onboard, the app communicates directly with your sensors and gateway for zero-latency control without relying on the cloud.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- How It Works Section -->
	<section class="how-it-works">
		<div class="container row-reverse-layout">
			<div class="content-side">
				<h2>The Hardware Ecosystem</h2>
				<p>Boat & Rv Guardian isn't just software; it's an orchestration of the best off-the-shelf smart hardware. We securely link Shelly Wi-Fi sensors to LinkTap gateways without relying on fragile third-party integrations.</p>
				<ul class="benefit-list">
					<li><strong>Free during beta, low-cost after:</strong> Enjoy the software for free during our beta phase, followed by a sustainable low-cost model.</li>
					<li><strong>Local API Mode:</strong> When you're onboard, the app communicates directly with your gateway for zero-latency control.</li>
					<li><strong>Cloud Fallback:</strong> When you leave the marina or campsite, cloud polling takes over seamlessly.</li>
				</ul>
				<a href="/components" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top: 1rem;">View Supported Components &rarr;</a>
			</div>
			<div class="image-side">
				<img src="/smart-hardware.png" alt="Smart Hardware Connection Abstract" class="feature-image" />
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA Section -->
	<section class="cta-section container">
		<div class="glass-card cta-card">
			<div class="cta-content">
				<h2>Ready to secure your rig?</h2>
				<p>Join the open-source community building better tools for digital nomads and mariners.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="cta-actions">
				<a href="https://github.com/jgearinger/Boat-RV-Guardian" class="btn btn-primary">View on GitHub</a>
				<a href="/components" class="btn btn-outline">See Supported Components</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* Hero Section */
	.hero {
		position: relative;
		padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.hero-bg-glow {
		position: absolute;
		top: -20%;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 800px;
		height: 800px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.15) 0%, rgba(11, 15, 25, 0) 70%);
		z-index: -1;
		border-radius: 50%;
	}

	.hero-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.badge {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
		background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3);
		color: var(--accent-color);
		border-radius: 20px;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.hero-title {
		font-size: 4rem;
		line-height: 1.1;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.hero-subtitle {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		max-width: 90%;
	}

	.hero-actions {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.hero-image-wrapper {
		position: relative;
		perspective: 1000px;
	}

	.hero-image {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
		transform: rotateY(-5deg) rotateX(5deg);
		transition: transform 0.5s ease;
		border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
	}

	.hero-image-wrapper:hover .hero-image {
		transform: rotateY(0) rotateX(0);
	}

	.glass-float {
		position: absolute;
		background: rgba(11, 15, 25, 0.6);
		backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
		animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.float-1 {
		top: 15%;
		left: -10%;
		animation-delay: 0s;
	}

	.float-2 {
		bottom: 15%;
		right: -10%;
		animation-delay: 2s;
	}

	.float-icon {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}

	.glass-float strong {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
	}

	.glass-float span {
		font-size: 0.8rem;
	}

	.status-alert { color: var(--danger-color); }
	.status-ok { color: var(--success-color); }

	@keyframes float {
		0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
		50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
		100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
	}

	/* Features Section */
	.features-section {
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
	}

	.section-header {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
	}

	.section-header h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.features-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.feature-card {
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
	}

	.feature-icon {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--surface-color);
		width: 60px;
		height: 60px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
	}

	.feature-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.feature-card p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	/* How It Works Layouts */
	.how-it-works {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
		padding: 6rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
	}

	.row-reverse-layout {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 4rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.content-side h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.content-side p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.benefit-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
	}

	.benefit-list li {
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--text-main);
	}

	.benefit-list li::before {
		content: "✓";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--accent-color);
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.benefit-list strong {
		color: #ffffff;
	}

	.feature-image {
		width: 100%;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
	}

	/* CTA Section */
	.cta-section {
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
	}

	.cta-card {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1), rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1));
		border-color: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3);
		padding: 4rem;
	}

	.cta-content h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.cta-content p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.cta-actions {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	/* Downloads Section */
	.downloads-section {
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--surface-border);
	}

	.downloads-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.download-card {
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: inherit;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
		display: block;
	}

	.download-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		border-color: var(--accent-color);
	}

	.download-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: #fff;
	}

	.download-card p {
		color: var(--text-muted);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 992px) {
		.hero-container, .row-reverse-layout {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			text-align: center;
		}
		
		.hero-subtitle {
			margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
		}
		
		.hero-actions {
			justify-content: center;
		}
		
		.glass-float {
			display: none; /* Hide floating elements on mobile for cleaner look */
		}
		
		.cta-card {
			flex-direction: column;
			text-align: center;
			gap: 2rem;
			padding: 2rem;
		}
		
		.benefit-list li {
			text-align: left;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.hero-title {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}
		.hero-actions {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
	}
</style>
